result.execSummary:
The defendant Kyle K. Ross was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Kyle K. Ross is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Kyle K. Ross was found guilty of Manuf/Deliver Amphetamine(<=3g) [Modifiers: Conspiracy to Commit], a class F felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(1)(e)1.
